anmu.org/数学" target="_blank">数学</a>生选择的是后一种；该系PhD项目本科毕业生可直接申请，无需相应的硕士学历。*(2)</p><p>该系基本上所有的学生均可以获得一定形式的奖学金，其形式主要包括Fellowship、<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/TA" target="_blank">TA</a>和<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/RA" target="_blank">RA</a>三种。第一年奖学金主要以Fellowship为主，第二年则主要以TA为主。该系奖学金无需单独申请，自动随Offer发放，所有入学新生都可以获得全额奖学金，包括全额的学费、医疗保险费以及外加按月发放的生活补助。*(1)(3)</p><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=orDtO5abLk7hGU_ZttttttiysgkEP8CpN-T_MThk3vaw2J8Y0fFXhC3YUrwQ0CnH4f3Q0C3S0znHegYMEdQsZWxOKY" target="_blank">FAQ for all applicants-Department of Biochemistry</a> UC Riverside</p><p>(2) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=qrTydPmDkbcX2zHq3bBIgVY9kDt80463yYHz29X8Pwhe5ioo2PIUo5L0ca_Lrj_crWr3HOHWyuDeCMIcghRz3_yumcwrHk_25NWyYHP_QR" target="_blank">The Master of Science Degree-Department of Biochemistry</a> UC Riverside</p><p>(3) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=brEVbykXku1DPCiVccccccbi6lUiHwqXlDESQsELF8LcMog64tefUhLgOjicF8gER_zqwWekjWukMQSKglqxj0rx8OHEayROXE" target="_blank">Financial Support and Expenses</a> UC Riverside</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3>生物学</h3><p><strong>基本信息：</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:17.9%">			<p><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/USNEWS排名" target="_blank">USNEWS排名</a></p>			</td>			<td style="width:11.64%">			<p>73</p>			</td>			<td style="width:13.3%">			<p>学费</p>			</td>			<td style="width:19.96%">			<p>$30,499</p>			</td>			<td style="width:18.3%">			<p>申请截止日期</p>			</td>			<td style="width:18.9%">			<p>12月1日</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:17.9%">			<p><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/TOEFL" target="_blank">TOEFL</a>要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:11.64%">			<p>80</p>			</td>			<td style="width:13.3%">			<p><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/GPA" target="_blank">GPA</a>要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:19.96%">			<p>无</p>			</td>			<td style="width:18.3%">			<p>可申请学期</p>			</td>			<td style="width:18.9%">			<p>秋季</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="wid