课程。*(2)</p><p>该专业向国际学生提供Fellowship、<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/TA" target="_blank">TA</a>、<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/RA" target="_blank">RA</a>等形式的奖学金，但具体金额及覆盖率不详。*(1)</p><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=lreSUwaUkRbTQj8FSm9zTX3UzjV6y_lUXsjom3GL_gHYHm28MmbCwNDnIaRQAePaFJq_gL47FPS" target="_blank">Entry Requirementss &amp; Financial Support for Prospective GGB Students</a> UC Riverside</p><p>(2) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=WrSJLFC5LjdAsiR3pppppp0UQH2SCFk_Wuxn7jYnLbTN6HY_WdTuQGjZLGOSZdiSvdMN6j2S9jFuJQaO" target="_blank">Entry requirements for the three GGB track</a> UC Riverside</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3>化学</h3><p><strong>基本信息：</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:17.9%">			<p><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/USNEWS排名" target="_blank">USNEWS排名</a></p>			</td>			<td style="width:11.64%">			<p>59</p>			</td>			<td style="width:13.3%">			<p>学费</p>			</td>			<td style="width:19.96%">			<p>$35,928</p>			</td>			<td style="width:18.3%">			<p>申请截止日期</p>			</td>			<td style="width:18.9%">			<p>1月5日</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:17.9%">			<p><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/TOEFL" target="_blank">TOEFL</a>要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:11.64%">			<p>80</p>			</td>			<td style="width:13.3%">			<p><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/GPA" target="_blank">GPA</a>要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:19.96%">			<p>无</p>			</td>			<td style="width:18.3%">			<p>可申请学期</p>			</td>			<td style="width:18.9%">			<p>秋季</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:17.9%">			<p><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/IELTS" target="_blank">IELTS</a>要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:11.64%">			<p>7.0</p>			</td>			<td style="width:13.3%">			<p><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/GRE" target="_blank">GRE</a>要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:19.96%">			<p>Required</p>			</td>			<td style="width:18.3%">			<p><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/GRE Subject" target="_blank">GRE Subject</a></p>			</td>			<td 