_blank">RA</a>等形式的奖学金，但不向冬季和春季学期的申请的国际学生发放，具体奖学金金额及覆盖率不详。该系要求所有自费的国际学生提供由银行开具的$46,000的<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/资金证明" target="_blank">资金证明</a>信。*(1)(5)</p><p><strong>专业设置</strong></p><ul>	<li>能源加工（Energy Processing）</li>	<li>空气质量与防火工程（Air Quality &amp; Fire Engineering）</li>	<li>微<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/纳米技术" target="_blank">纳米工程</a>（Nano &amp; Micro Scale Engineering）</li>	<li>计算与设计（Computation &amp; Design）</li>	<li>材料特性与加工（Materials Properties &amp; Processing）</li>	<li>多相流动与燃烧（Multiphase Flow &amp; Combustion）</li>	<li>生物应用（Bio-Applications）*(6)</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=2rNMmQLtkO9fNvioMj4qMa3MaMc2aXZP65GNu-HQPK94qMcoE3dIw4dnenYjaq8Nh4TRpq4oA4tSR_5C5V60pP-78LujU0_1ZRnYDP83Qa" target="_blank">Admission Requirements &amp; Financial Support-ME</a> UC Riverside</p><p>(2)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=lreSUwjbw4VCAYQ7_gY1qIdRrBowL6kBsSd3FpVYFbMcJwd-ldEBsu3PkyhmDJBQaKW1VV7vVOGSh02QS1MiZBW6G3LL-EhNxBBQST2BV6NSVVEd1g67rVh_EzsuyyCm7rfKpuCoeq" target="_blank">Current Quarter Tuition and Fees</a> UC Riverside</p><p>(3)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=8rL6TCN8kyji7M9bvvvvvvMKWI7X392YololnxmGVxDOouzG5IDYornTo_hG5_7KJG5qr0hT29_T8RqV2jmVAoBnIik" target="_blank">Graduate Deadlines</a> UC Riverside</p><p>(4) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=IrnDV7pTwdft_3lEggggggQke_8ACbPsXlzFzFnCEZTtu35vgaU5DOxpasAkLS8RLp8xKYEBPyFqG2P1AgypYzlvylC" target="_blank">Master of Science (M.S.) Program-ME</a> UC Riverside</p><p>(5) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=frh1ZEbnL9PXWja-4E4yyEtXrBPO9Br-PefoP85SwdvxZAVWPtml6JFvmWrpc7SNVXuavinJnsvEtsznKVFALwCeJLl_nLr2gupu-0gqxgJj" target="_blank">APPLICATION CHECKLIST-ME</a> UC Riverside</p><p>(6) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=grPZ_x32wjNSr8N_PPPPPPn9cXoHl0-ItutuFj3J1jSVtLdV_9ueqxe4BiTD_9t3Nxkg" target="_blank">Research Area Clusters-ME</a> UC Riverside</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2>医学院</h2><p>加州大学河滨分校<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/医学"