i>管理信息系统（Management <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/信息系统管理" target="_blank">Information Systems</a>）</li>	<li>管理科学与<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/运营管理" target="_blank">运营管理</a>（Management Science/<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/运营管理" target="_blank">Operations</a> Management）</li>	<li><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/市场营销" target="_blank">市场营销</a>（<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/市场营销" target="_blank">Marketing</a>）*(4)</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=mrtw23K-LUrJdoihNNNNNNLXtru7-W_UT6I7TuBOD4pULlyOeikjL6GpoTRxVjljB5yLB_ZP0dsZS" target="_blank">How to Apply-MBA</a> UC Riverside</p><p>(2)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=mrtw23uUws9rfUyZuuuuuHqQv2yYfZVQiBHef67fjI0tcA3vzaxWC14uQlU625OSiQSCpOh4Fnel-lvrTj8rp-BiN7_tIKGOe_35WcKwcvCIaLCIxhfj5CDhoyPnoLm_4i" target="_blank">Current Quarter Tuition and Fees</a> UC Riverside</p><p>(3)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=OrMxo-DGLmpEbjSfFFFFFFDpZMtTeh6yGItPUotrv7lTsAa3P_Mw5kRPs8BWK0AOS1AgrfI5bjr5rZpm8E9gA6QI2S" target="_blank">Profile of 2015-2016&nbsp;Entering Class-MBA</a> UC Riverside</p><p>(4)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=2rNMmQLYkmG0lag0ttttttmTS6O4amcLhnqLJRqC83CMAWdX4nT1hXUbF0JRhIpoW7pNFzFEW23orPjTcqwb2H-GHz_4bu" target="_blank">MBA-Electives</a> UC Riverside</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3>会计硕士</h3><p><strong>基本信息：</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:17.16%">			<p><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/USNEWS排名" target="_blank">USNEWS排名</a></p>			</td>			<td style="width:14.34%">			<p>89</p>			</td>			<td style="width:20.7%">			<p>学费</p>			</td>			<td style="width:14.34%">			<p>$1,103/学分</p>			</td>			<td style="width:19.12%">			<p>申请截止日期</p>			</td>			<td style="width:14.34%">			<p>5月1日</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:17.16%">			<p><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/TOEFL" target="_blank">TOEFL</a>要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:14.34%">			<p>80</p>			</td>			<td style="width:20.